agave.internal
Interface HandlerDescriptor

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<HandlerDescriptor>
All Known Implementing Classes:
HandlerDescriptorImpl
public interface HandlerDescriptor
extends java.lang.Comparable<HandlerDescriptor>

A descriptor that aggregates information about the handler so that the configured filter can efficiently route an HTTP request into the handler that this object describes. The specific information that implementing objects of this interface aggregate are:

  • URIPattern
  • Handler Class
  • Handler Method
    • Form Class
      • Parameter Binders
        • Converters
  • HttpServletRequest Binder
  • HttpServletResponse Binder

Author:
Damian Carrillo
